with info    home http://plasma.kde.org/
with info    cite 'MLDonkey integration for KDE

kmldonkey integrate MLDonkey into KDE.
It provides the following features:

ED2K link handling in Konqueror
Konqueror service menu for adding all links on a web page
Control Centre module for configuring how to talk to MLDonkey
A panel applet for Kicker that displays mldonkey status'
